## Discipline

- Each material references brand.md for tokens (colors, type) —
  not hardcoded copies.
- Source files live in design tools; this file holds the spec +
  pointer.
- Version each material when redesigned — keep older versions
  referenced for legacy artifacts.
- Print orders pause if `brand.md` is mid-update — wait for the
  ADR to land before re-ordering.

